    com.fasterxml.jackson.core.Versioned, Serializable

    public class FacebookModule
extends com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.module.SimpleModule
    Jackson module for setting up mixin annotations on Facebook model types. This enables the use of Jackson annotations without directly annotating the model classes themselves.
